图片来源：Kyoto News“ 全球新冠肺炎疫情播报，持续更新。
Source: Kyoto News, "Global Newly Crowded Pneumonia: An Update."
”全球0800【全球疫情汇总】据新浪实时统计，截至3月9日8点，除中国（包括港澳台地区）以外，海外新冠肺炎累计确诊28854例，死亡702例，治愈2996例。
A total of 28,854 new cases of pneumonia were diagnosed, 702 died and 2,996 cured as of 0800 March in China, including Hong Kong, Macao and Taiwan, according to Sina real-time statistics.
数据来源：新浪0800【世卫组织：全球超过100个国家地区出现新冠肺炎病例】当地时间3月8日，世卫组织发布最新一期新冠肺炎情况每日报告。
Source: Sina 0800 [WHO: new cases of pneumonia in more than 100 countries worldwide] The WHO released its latest daily report on pneumonia on March 8, local time.
截至欧洲中部时间3月8日上午10时（北京时间17时），中国境外共101个国家/领地/地区确诊新冠肺炎24727例（新增3610例），死亡共计484例（新增71例），新增8个国家/领地/地区（保加利亚、哥斯达黎加、法罗群岛、法属圭亚那、马尔代夫、马耳他、马提尼克、摩尔多瓦）出现新冠肺炎病例。
As of 10: 00 a.m. Central European Time (17: 00 Beijing time), a total of 24,727 cases (3,610 new cases) and 484 new deaths (71 new cases) had been diagnosed outside China, and 8 new cases (Bulgaria, Costa Rica, Faroe Islands, French Guyana, Maldives, Malta, Martinique, Moldova) had been reported.
意大利0800【新增新冠肺炎1492例，累计确诊7375例】根据当地时间3月8日18时意大利卫生部公布的最近数据，意大利累计确诊感染新冠病毒总人数为7375例，较3月7日18时新增1492例，新增133例死亡病例，累积死亡366例，治愈622例。
Italy has reported a cumulative total of 7,375 new cases of new crown pneumonia at 18: 00 pm local time, an increase of 1,492 new cases, a cumulative total of 133 deaths, 366 cumulative deaths and 622 cures, according to the latest figures released by the Italian Ministry of Health on March 8, 2008.
0800【陆军参谋长确诊】意大利陆军参谋长萨尔瓦多莱·法利纳8日下午发表声明称，他本人病毒核酸检测呈阳性，目前正在自己的居所内隔离。
0800 [Army Chief of Staff confirmed] Italian Army Chief of Staff Salvadoran Falina said in a statement on the afternoon that he himself tested positive for nucleic acid and is being quarantined in his own home.
法利纳在声明中说，他将继续履行自己的职责，但需要他本人出席的工作将由另外一名将军代替。
In his statement, Mr. Farina said he would continue to carry out his duties, but that work that required his personal presence would be replaced by another general.
韩国0800【新增179例新冠确诊病例，累计7313例为海外第二】伊朗0800【累积确诊6566例】伊朗卫生部宣布，截至当地时间8日上午，伊朗新冠肺炎确诊病例新增743例，累计病例数升至6566例，其中死亡194例。
South Korea 0800 [179 new cases confirmed, 7,313 overseas second) Iran 0800 [cumulative confirmed 6,566 cases] The Iranian Ministry of Health announced 743 new cases of confirmed cases of new crown pneumonia in Iran as of the morning of August 8, 2006, bringing the total number of cases to 6,566, including 194 deaths.
法国0800【累计确诊1126例】据法国卫生部最新通报，截至当地时间8日下午3时，法国新冠肺炎患者累计确诊1126例，较昨日新增177例，总计死亡病例19例。
France confirmed 1,126 cases of pneumonia at 3: 00 pm local time, 177 more than the previous day, bringing the total number of deaths to 19, the Ministry of Health said.
法国卫生部长韦朗表示，目前法国疫情警戒仍处于第二阶段，将竭尽全力应对疫情。
France's health minister said the French epidemic alert is still in the second phase, will do everything possible to deal with the outbreak.
韦朗同时宣布法国将禁止所有1000人以上聚集活动。
He also announced that France would ban all gatherings of more than 1,000 people.
0800【国民议会确诊病例增至6例】据法国法兰西岛大区卫生局3月8日通报，法国国民议会新冠肺炎确诊病例增至6例，其中4例为议员，2例为内部工作人员。
0800 [Cases confirmed by the National Assembly have increased to 6 cases] The French National Assembly's new crown pneumonia has been confirmed in six cases, four of them by members of parliament and two by internal staff, the Regional Health Directorate of Ile-de-France reported on March 8.
所有确诊病例均已被隔离。
All confirmed cases have been isolated.
德国0800【累积超900例，卫生部长建议取消大型活动】德国疾控机构罗伯特·科赫研究所公布的最新数据显示，截至当地时间8日15时，德国累计确诊新冠肺炎病例升至902例，较前一日增加107例。
Germany's top 100 confirmed cases of new crown pneumonia rose to 902 by 1500 local time, 107 more than the previous day, according to the latest figures released by the German CDC's Robert Koch Institute.
其中北威州、巴符州和巴伐利亚州疫情严重。
Of these, North Wales, BWW and Bavaria have severe epidemics.
德国卫生部长延斯·施潘8日建议取消所有1000人以上的大型活动。
German Health Minister Jens Schpan 8 proposed to cancel all large-scale events with more than 1,000 people.
美国0800【累积确诊超500例】据CNN3月8日报道，根据美国国家和地方卫生机构、政府以及美国疾控中心的数据，美国新冠肺炎确诊病例增至521例，其中21人死亡。
The number of confirmed cases of pneumonia in the United States rose to 521, with 21 deaths, according to national and local health authorities, the government and the U.S. Centers for Disease Control and Prevention.
日本0800【国内累计确诊480例】截至日本当地时间3月8日22时，日本当天新增33例新冠肺炎患者，累计确诊480例，死亡7人。
Japan confirmed 480 cases of pneumonia on March 8, 2008 at 2200 hours local time in Japan, with a cumulative total of 480 confirmed cases and 7 deaths.
此外，“钻石公主”号邮轮累计确诊696例，累计死亡7人；包机回国日侨累计确诊14例。
In addition, a total of 696 cases were diagnosed and 7 people died. A total of 14 cases were confirmed by chartered flights.
西班牙0800【患者累计确诊病例至613人】死亡17例。
Spain 0800 cumulative confirmed cases to 613 cases of death 17.
首都马德里确诊207例。
207 cases were diagnosed in Madrid.
瑞士0800【累计确诊281例】截至3月8日中午12点，瑞士全境共确诊新冠肺炎281例，比前一天增长71例。
By 12 noon on March 8, 281 new cases of pneumonia had been confirmed across Switzerland, an increase of 71 cases over the previous day.
所有新冠肺炎确诊病例均被隔离。
All confirmed cases of new crown pneumonia were isolated.
联邦卫生部呼吁民众在排队和会议期间保持距离。
The Federal Ministry of Health calls on people to distance themselves between queues and meetings.
英国0800【累计确诊273例】3月8日，英国新增新冠肺炎感染者67人，总确诊人数达273人 。
Britain added 67 new cases of pneumonia on March 8, bringing the total number of confirmed cases to 273.
这也是英国发现病例以来单日最大增幅。
This is the biggest increase in a single day since cases were discovered in Britain.
荷兰0800【累计确诊265例】荷兰公共卫生和环境研究所3月8日发布消息，该国当天新增77例新冠肺炎确诊病例，荷兰新冠肺炎确诊病例累计265例，其中144例是在国外感染 。
Dutch Institute of Public Health and the Environment confirmed 77 new cases of pneumonia on the same day, the Netherlands reported 265 confirmed cases of new crown pneumonia, 144 of which were infections abroad, the Dutch Institute of Public Health and the Environment said.
目前，该国已有3名患者死亡，均为80岁以上的男性。
Currently, three patients have died in the country, all men over 80 years of age.
瑞典0800【累积确诊超200例】当地时间3月8日，瑞典《晚报》报道，瑞典新增42例新冠肺炎确诊病例，累计确诊203例。
Sweden's Evening News reported 42 new confirmed cases of pneumonia in Sweden, with a cumulative total of 203 cases, the Swedish Evening News reported Monday.
越南0800【累计确诊30例】越南卫生部8日晚间宣布，越南新增9例新冠肺炎确诊病例，全国累计确诊病例增至30例。
Vietnam's Ministry of Health announced Tuesday night that 9 new cases of pneumonia have been confirmed in Vietnam, bringing the total number of confirmed cases nationwide to 30.
沙特阿拉伯0800【东部卡提夫地区封城】卡提夫是沙特东部省什叶派穆斯林聚居区之一。
Saudi Arabia 0800 [Eastern Katif Area Sealed] Katif is one of the Shiite Muslim colonies in the Eastern Province of Saudi Arabia.
沙特卫生部公布的消息显示，目前沙特境内已发现的新冠肺炎确诊病例为11例，其中多数为近期曾前往伊朗旅行的东部省居民。
According to information released by the Saudi Ministry of Health, 11 confirmed cases of new crown pneumonia have been detected in Saudi Arabia, most of which are residents of the Eastern Province who have recently travelled to Iran.
阿根廷0800【累计确诊12例 尚无本地传播】当地时间3月8日，阿根廷卫生部确认新增3例新冠肺炎病例，全国累计病例达12例。
Argentina confirmed 3 new cases of crown pneumonia on March 8, 2006, 12 cases nationwide, according to the Ministry of Health.
最新确认的三例病人目前都在医院隔离，其中两人生活在首都布宜诺斯艾利斯。
The three newly confirmed cases are currently being quarantined in hospitals, two of whom live in the capital, Buenos Aires.
与此前的9位患者一样，这三人刚刚从欧洲或美国返回，均属于输入型病例。
Like the previous nine patients, the three had just returned from Europe or the United States and were imported cases.
南非0800【首例患者已痊愈】南非卫生部长穆凯兹8日晚间透露，在经过四天治疗后，南非首个新型冠状病毒肺炎确诊患者已经康复，目前只需官方解除警报即可回家。
South Africa's first confirmed case of coronavirus pneumonia has recovered after four days of treatment and now only needs an official warning to return home, South Africa's health minister said Tuesday night.
该患者是一名38岁南非男性，此前与妻子等共计10人一同前往意大利旅行，3月1日回到位于南非家中。
The patient, a 38-year-old South African man, had travelled to Italy with his wife and 10 others before returning to his home in South Africa on 1 March.
